Q: 在2024年24/7 Jet Inc.的前五大目的地国家（按航班量排序）有哪些？
SQL:
SELECT
        arr_country_id,
        arr_country_name,
        count(*) AS num
FROM
        zts_plane_flight_1 a
        JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
WHERE
        a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
        AND '2024-12'
        AND b.supplier_id = "1001"
GROUP BY
        arr_country_id,
        arr_country_name
ORDER BY
        num DESC
        LIMIT 5;
actual_SQL:
SELECT
        arr_country_id,
        arr_country_name,
        count(*) AS num
FROM
        zts_plane_flight_1 a
        JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
